          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Student Loan Fair Prepayment Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to set forth how a student loan borrower's prepayment amount on a Federal Family Education Loan, Federal Direct Loan, or Federal Perkins Loan must be applied. </p> <p> <p>]]></text>
